<!--
  Laxora demo content (WXR 1.2)
  Imports:
   - 13 fleet vehicles (laxora_vehicle CPT) with categories + specs
   - 6 fleet categories (vehicle_category taxonomy)

  How to import:
   WP Admin → Tools → Import → WordPress → Install / Run Importer
   Upload this file. Assign content to your admin user. Click "Submit".
   Then visit "Tools → Regenerate Thumbnails" if needed.

  NOTE: Featured images are referenced by external URL. After import, you can
  bulk-download them with the "Auto Upload Images" plugin so they live in your
  Media Library. Or simply rely on the standalone Laxora theme which already
  bundles every image at /assets/images/fleet/.
-->
